      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to simplified geometries. Full pump geometry code verification not completed.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Numerical code verification must demonstrate order-of-accuracy confirmation via MMS on representative rotating-frame geometry with documented residual norms below 1e-6 for all transported quantities, satisfying ASME V&V 40 Gradation 4 requirements at MRL 5."
    },
