      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence index computed across three mesh refinements. GCI values acceptable for velocity fields but hemolysis-specific QoI convergence not fully demonstrated.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Discretization error must be quantified via GCI on at least three systematically refined meshes with refinement ratio >= 1.3, achieving GCI < 5% on the primary hemolysis index QoI, consistent with Gradation 4 at MRL 5."
