      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "QoIs include normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) and modified index of hemolysis (MIH). These are clinically relevant but the mapping from CFD shear stress history to hemolysis model output introduces model-form uncertainty not fully addressed."
    },
